'''Settlement 32''' was a [[Senate Select Committee for Refugees|SELCORE]] refugee camp on [[Duro/Legends|Duro]] in [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]]. It contained [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]], [[Vor]]s, and [[Vuvrian/Legends|Vuvrians]]. Its administrator was [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], who was assisted by his son [[Darth Caedus|Jacen]] and the [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]] [[Droma]]. Settlement 32 was destroyed by [[naotebe wingling]]s, [[Insect/Legends|insects]] created by [[Nom Anor]] that ate the domes of the camp, shortly before the [[Battle of Duro (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Duro]].<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Balance Point">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref>

